WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:04.120 --> 00:00:06.560
Hello. My name is Alexander Parisot.

00:00:06.640 --> 00:00:08.120
Welcome to Bologne, France.

00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:11.800
Here is the brand-new FH
decorated as a tribute to Rihanna.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:22.280
I love her music.
I love everything about her.

00:00:23.360 --> 00:00:26.680
On this side
we have two photographs,

00:00:26.760 --> 00:00:29.880
one of her face
and one is a full-length portrait.

00:00:29.960 --> 00:00:32.920
This photo was taken at a Rihanna gig.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:37.480
This is the R of Rihanna's name.
I think I prefer this side.

00:00:41.400 --> 00:00:45.840
At the back we added an extra light
to make it look nicer,

00:00:45.920 --> 00:00:48.920
with a reference
to the stainless steel bar on the side.

00:00:50.280 --> 00:00:56.080
In this image you can see the details
very well, such as her eyes,

00:00:56.160 --> 00:00:58.160
her nail polish, her shoes.

00:00:59.560 --> 00:01:02.200
We also added a console at the back

00:01:02.280 --> 00:01:06.480
in order to create a feeling of unity.

00:01:06.560 --> 00:01:12.640
We placed red LEDs on it,
as well as around the cab.

00:01:12.720 --> 00:01:17.320
The truck has 74 LEDs in total.

00:01:17.400 --> 00:01:21.240
When they're all lit,
it's reminiscent of her stage shows.

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:27.800
For me,
the truck is at its best at dusk,

00:01:27.880 --> 00:01:31.680
when the LEDs
make the whole vehicle stand out.

00:01:31.760 --> 00:01:34.200
It brings tears to my eyes.

00:01:45.480 --> 00:01:48.560
At first the truck was meant to be red,

00:01:48.640 --> 00:01:52.400
like it is now but without
the paintings, just plain red.

00:01:52.480 --> 00:01:59.400
For my 40th birthday, I had a big party
and planned a trip to America.

00:01:59.480 --> 00:02:04.640
And at the last moment I decided,
with my wife, to have the truck painted.

00:02:04.720 --> 00:02:08.160
So it was my 40th birthday present.

00:02:08.240 --> 00:02:14.480
For me, driving a decorated truck
is a childhood dream,

00:02:14.560 --> 00:02:16.560
having seen decorated trucks go by.

00:02:16.640 --> 00:02:19.240
It's my dream come true.

00:02:19.320 --> 00:02:22.480
What's more, this theme
has never been done on any vehicle.

00:02:22.560 --> 00:02:26.200
The Rihanna theme had never been done
on any other truck.

00:02:26.280 --> 00:02:31.160
It's the first ever truck
decorated with Rihanna's image.

00:02:31.240 --> 00:02:35.520
This is my album of the Rihanna show
in June 2013.

00:02:35.600 --> 00:02:38.280
I went to her show
at the Stade de France with my wife.

00:02:38.360 --> 00:02:41.640
Here you see the Stade de France
and the ticket.

00:02:41.720 --> 00:02:44.520
And inside there are various photos
of the show.

00:02:44.600 --> 00:02:49.880
Now I'm going to play you an excerpt
of my favourite Rihanna song.

